<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>TripSpin</title>
    <meta name="description" content="TripSpin is the first of its kind travel concierge. Plan your trip today!">
    <style>
        body, html {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            height: 100%;
            overflow: hidden;
            background-color: #000;
            color: #fff;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }
        iframe {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            border: none;
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        .seo-content {
            position: absolute;
            width: 1px;
            height: 1px;
            padding: 0;
            margin: -1px;
            overflow: hidden;
            clip: rect(0, 0, 0, 0);
            white-space: nowrap;
            border: 0;
            z-index: 0;
        }
        .loading-fallback {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            flex-direction: column;
            background-color: #000;
            z-index: 0;
        }
        .loading-fallback h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        .loading-fallback p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            max-width: 80%;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Visible loading fallback for crawlers and users with slow connections -->
    <div class="loading-fallback">
        <h1>TripSpin</h1>
        <p>Travel isn't changing, but the way you plan your travel will never be the same.</p>
        <p>Loading 3D Earth Animation...</p>
    </div>
    
    <!-- SEO-friendly content that's visually hidden but available to crawlers -->
    <div class="seo-content">
        <h1>TripSpin</h1>
        <p>TripSpin is the first of its kind travel concierge. Plan your trip today!</p>
        <p>Explore destinations worldwide with our interactive 3D Earth animation.</p>
        <p>Join our Early Access program to receive updates and be the first to experience TripSpin.</p>
    </div>
    
    <iframe src="earth-animation.html" title="TripSpin"></iframe>
</body>
</html>
